<%= h2_with_anchor "Best Practices" %>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Preprocess Text</strong>: Clean and normalize text before storing embeddings</li>
    <li><strong>Use Descriptive Metadata</strong>: Include relevant metadata for filtering and debugging</li>
    <li><strong>Monitor Cache Hit Rates</strong>: Track cache effectiveness and adjust TTL accordingly</li>
    <li><strong>Batch Operations</strong>: Store embeddings in batches rather than one at a time</li>
    <li><strong>Version Your Embeddings</strong>: Include model version in metadata when upgrading models</li>
</ol>

<div class="alert alert-warning">
    <p><strong>Important:</strong> When changing embedding models or dimensions, you must recreate the embeddings table as vectors are not compatible across different models or dimensions.</p>
</div>